          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-X32-14H1-headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-X32-14H1-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-X32-14H1-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-X32-14H1-line-1" n="1"><hi rend="display-initial">D</hi>EAR dean, since you in sleepy wise</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X32-14H1-line-2" n="2">Have op'd your mouth, and clos'd your eyes.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X32-14H1-line-3" n="3">Like Ghost I glide along your floor,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X32-14H1-line-4" n="4">And softly shut the parlour door:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X32-14H1-line-5" n="5">For should I break your sweet repose,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X32-14H1-line-6" n="6">Who knows what money you might lose?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X32-14H1-line-7" n="7">Since oftentimes it has been found,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X32-14H1-line-8" n="8">A dream has giv'n ten thousand pound.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X32-14H1-line-9" n="9">Then sleep, my friend, dear dean, sleep on,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X32-14H1-line-10" n="10">And all you get shall be your own;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X32-14H1-line-11" n="11">Provided you to this agree,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X32-14H1-line-12" n="12">That all you lose belongs to me.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
